§ `Jurisdiction Library`

-- Library for representing jurisdictions (countries, regions, states, municipalities)
-- Uses ISO 3166-1 codes (alpha-2 and alpha-3) for countries
-- Uses ISO 3166-2 codes for subdivisions
-- Version 1.0.0 (2024-12-16)

§§ `Version`

`Jurisdiction Library Version` MEANS "1.0.0"
`Jurisdiction Library Date` MEANS "2024-12-16"


